entries.femaleVariant: Found two of 'em yesterday. Right 'round here, not even swole up yet. Lead to the skull.
Way it is. Maybe today we'll get a better catch.
Yep. Gangs got 'em. Ain't nobody gonna come for 'em after.
Grabbed a few things off 'em, then left 'em on the sand. Tide should wash 'em out.
Found one yesterday, too. Naked, gutted for chrome. Fishes already gnawin' at the holes in 'er.
